content:
Ukraine is the world's largest supplier of sunflower oil and Indians consume ~15% of it.

PM Vajpayee imported 3.1 lakh tonnes of sunflower oil in 2001-02. PM Modi imported 20 lakh tonnes of it, last year.

75% of it comes from Ukraine. Most of the rest from Russia.
